<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Brotherhood" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Brotherhood,</orth> 1) quality and love of a brother: <cit><quote>finds b. in thee no sharper spur?</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.2.9" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 2, 9</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.1.114" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 1, 114</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.1.55" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 1, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.111" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 111</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.1.108" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 108</bibl>.<lb />2) association, corporation: <cit><quote>degrees in schools and --s in cities,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 104</bibl></cit>. Religious order: <cit><quote>by my b.!</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 5.2.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 2, 17</bibl></cit>.
